data.description: Welcome to your dream Chicago bungalow in wonderful Portage Park! This charming 4 bed, 1.5 bath gem offers the perfect blend of classic design and modern amenities. Spacious primary bedroom can fit a king size bed. Step inside to a warm and inviting living room, bathed in natural light; perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. Beautifully updated kitchen will spark your culinary creativity; from dinner parties to family meals. Finished basement is the perfect family room. Spacious fenced-in yard is perfect for outdoor gatherings, gardening, and playtime and 2-car garage. Updated furnace (2020) with central heating, providing enhanced efficiency and peace of mind. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful Chicago bungalow your forever home.
